articles.title: Kevin Strickland, wrongfully convicted of triple murder, freed after more than four decades in prison
articles.description: A Missouri man who has spent more than four decades in prison for a triple murder will walk free after a judge exonerated him Tuesday.
articles.content:
A Missouri man who has spent more than four decades in prison for a triple murder walked out of prison a free man Tuesday after a judge exonerated him hours earlier.
